snippet.title: Mannequin The Spotting Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2451140/Mannequin_The_Spotting/
---------------------------------------------
Trailer for the upcoming sequel to Mannequin The Passing, this is Mannequin The Spotting, coming in 2023 exclusively to Steam.

Can you escape the Mannequins?
Use security cameras to find the evil Mannequins hiding among the others by observing any changes to their body. Mark the Mannequins as you need to, and then walk through them to find the exit without getting too close to the evil Mannequins.

Featuring 7 different game play modes,  20 stages with 10 different themes, hidden items to change the cosmetics of the Mannequins and more!

Visit the Steam page now and wish-list to keep follow announcements.
